__________________________________<br>
<br>
Now, is it worth the effort for 15 items with 5 charges of lower level spells?  Not to me.  But perhaps there is some benefit to be found by doing the ones which allow you access to other classes spells.  A necro might love 5 charges of Phantom chain.  Or magicians might like 5 charges of Group resist magic.  Maybe the enchanter would like the 5 charges of elemental armor.  And so on. . .  <br>
<br>
You be the judge.<br>
